description: AMUNDI EUR CORPORATE BOND 1-5Y ESG UCITS ETF Acc seeks to replicate, as closely as possible, whether the trend is rising or falling, the performance of the Bloomberg MSCI ESG Euro Corporate 1-5 Year Select Index (the "Index"), and to minimize the tracking error between the net asset value of the Sub-Fund and the performance of the Index. The anticipated level of tracking error, under normal market conditions, is indicated in the prospectus of the Sub-Fund. For further information, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
name: Amundi EUR Corporate Bond 1-5Y ESG UCITS ETF Acc
